Package: ppmData
Type: Package
Title: Quasirandom quardature scheme using dirichlet tesselation for species Poisson point process models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Skipton", "Woolley", email = "skipton.woolley@unimelb.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Scott", "Foster", email = "scott.foster@csiro.au", role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: Skipton Woolley <skipton.woolley@unimelb.edu.au>
Description: This package generates a set of quasi-random points for a quadrature scheme, we calculate each points weights using a voronoi algorithm. The result data.frames from the function calls in this package will enable users to pass these datasets to existing single and multiple species models inorder to extend them to Point Processes.
License: GPL-3
